This paper deals with the detection of malicious behavior using machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of data analysis and statistical methods, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the implementation and maintenance of security systems, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of data streams, which is a common topic in data science (cs.DS).
